main event: A witness in Schenectady, New York reported seeing an unidentified object with a dome and a bright light on February 9, 1967.
interesting points: The object had a dome on top and a round light that shone from within.
The object reflected a bright sheen down behind some trees.
The object disappeared at a tremendous speed without any sound or trail.
The witness had seen similar objects on previous occasions.
The witness requested more information from Project Blue Book on how to report and follow up on such sightings.
sighted object: A dome-shaped object with a bright round light
